# Flash Sale Task

## Overview
This repository contains a minimal Flash Sale system built with **Laravel & SQL Server**, including migrations, models, and tests to demonstrate key functionality:

## Migrations & Seeders
All migrations are in `database/migrations`:

- `create_users_table`
- `create_products_table`
- `create_holds_table`
- `create_orders_table`
- `create_personal_access_tokens_table`

Seeders are optional. Minimal test data can be inserted using **Tinker**:

```bash
php artisan tinker


EXAMPLE:

$user = \App\Models\User::create(['name'=>'Test User','email'=>'test@example.com','password'=>bcrypt('password')]);
$product = \App\Models\Product::create(['name'=>'Test Product','price'=>100,'total_stock'=>10,'available_stock'=>10]);
$hold = \App\Models\Hold::create(['product_id'=>$product->id,'qty'=>5,'expires_at'=>now()->addDay()]);
$order = \App\Models\Order::create(['product_id'=>$product->id,'hold_id'=>$hold->id,'user_id'=>$user->id,'qty'=>2,'total'=>200,'status'=>'pending']);
